The AppleScript backend, parsers, repository abstractions, approval system,
domain tool classes, and supporting utilities in this repository are a
near-verbatim port from the upstream project. The MCP server entrypoint has
been replaced with a CLI entrypoint (`olk`) and a disk-backed approval store
to make the same surface area usable from a single-shot terminal binary.

